      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MHN
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     J
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     L
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     ADD  1         J
     C           AY,J      IFEQ ','
     C                     LEAVE
